She kept the gun aimed at Dracona.
"I see the symbol, but I'll need verification."
She opened her commlink to Megatron's frequency only.
"Commander Megatron. This is DarkMouse. I have a Predacon here who 
says that you authorized access into the base. Named Dracona. Waiting 
for confermation Commander."
